reviews_data.review_text: Drinks and food were delicious! Drinks came out super fast and the customer service was amazing
The drinks are really good! Especially the Longan series, light but flavorful tastes. Definitely will come back for another drink!
Super services! The food and drinks were beyond amazing. I love the location too. Right in the middle of Plaza Midwood so you can explore the area with boba!!
What a pleasure  . I been wait for this location open over half year . Great place nice staff really good food  .
Best bubble tea, korean fried chicken and spicy chicken sandwich in town !
My favorite bubble tea place and the best fried chicken in town!!! Must order the chicken sandwich and fried chickens. Drink I recommend all fruit teas and brown sugar bubble tea! 5 stars!!!

Wonderful tea cafe with lots to offer! I love the environment and how there are so many drinks to choose from with reasonable prices! Once you make a purchase, you get a free cute key chain and a lovely Tsaocaa small bag, it's so cute! I definitely will be coming here often!❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️

I ordered fried chicken - cheesy, sweet and spicy, brown sugar milk tea, and mango sago. Mango sago could get better. It can be sweater and more flavorful. However, I was satisfied with overall quality of food and service.

Absolutely loved this place! The egg waffle was delicious and the drinks were amazing. The shop itself is beautiful, with a great vibe. So happy Charlotte finally has a location, will definitely be back!

This place has great drink options and food, something for everyone! The chicken sandwich was fresh and tender and the fries were good too! Also the springs rolls were very good. Excited to try other stuff on the menu. Cute displays and knick knacks throughout the shop. There's additional street parking nearby in the neighborhood.
I got the ruby black milk tea and it's so good! You can really taste the tea and the boba is made well. The employees are very friendly!

This was the best chicken sandwich I’ve ever had, and I used to work a Chick-fil-A! Gabe took my order with accuracy and swiftness and made my drink with extra care and love in his heart! I also loved the labubu tree and I hope it stays around for awhile!

We have been waiting for this spot to open and it did not disappoint! Hannah and the team were awesome and took the time to anwer all my questions. We found out their chicken was HALAL!!!! We tried their Thai tea and boneless chicken. The Thai tea was too sweet so definitely would lower the sugar level next time but was delicious. The fried chicken was CRISPY and delicious. I look forward to spreading the word!

OMG…. Never thought a chicken sandwich can be so Juicyyyyy. Not only that the outside is crispy, the inside…. Good portion/price too.

Friendly service, great product, definitely will be my go to.
So tasty and delicious food. Super cozy and wonderful environment. I’ll definitely back.
Love this place, came on opening day and everyone was very friendly and drinks/food was very good!! 10/10 would recommend!!
The dumplings and boneless chicken are great!
I had such a wonderful experience here, the mango yogurt slush was soooooo good! The atmosphere was very pleasant and welcoming and the service was spectacular! 10/10 would recommend.

I personally highly recommend this place! The food is incredibly delicious. The fried chicken is absolutely perfect – it is unbelievably tender and juicy on the inside, and crispy outside. The drink that I order is also fantastic. Meanwhile, the dining area is very clean and fancy.
